text: Mohamed Sobhy (; born 15 July 1999) is an Egyptian professional footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Egyptian League club Zamalek. ==Honours== ===Zamalek=== *Egypt Cup: 2018–19 *Egyptian Super Cup: 2019–20 * CAF Super Cup: 2020 ===Egypt=== *Africa U-23 Cup of Nations Champions: 2019 ===Individual=== *2019 Africa U-23 Cup of Nations Best Goalkeeper ==References== ==External links== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Egyptian footballers Category:Zamalek SC players Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:Petrojet SC players
